---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Contact | 聯絡我">
	<section class="py-24 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-12">Contact</h1>
		<div class="space-y-8 text-zinc-400">
			<p class="text-lg">如果您有任何拍攝需求或合作想法，歡迎透過以下方式與我聯繫：</p>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div>
					<span class="block text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-600 mb-1">Email</span>
					<a href="mailto:example@email.com" class="text-2xl text-white hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity underline decoration-zinc-800 underline-offset-8">example@email.com</a>
				</div>
				<div>
					<span class="block text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-600 mb-1">Social</span>
					<a href="#" class="text-2xl text-white hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity">Instagram</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
